OL,3,CStrike ballot launched at university
OL,4,Cover proposed job cuts
OL,6,FA ballot on strike action at a
OL,7,Funiversity has been launched by a
OL,8,Funion that represents lecturers in
OL,9,Fresponse to upcoming redundancies.
OL,11,FThe Educational Institute of
OL,12,FScotland's (EIS) University Lecturers'
OL,13,FAssociation (ULA) branch at the
OL,14,FUniversity of the West of Scotland
OL,15,F(UWS) said on Monday it had launched
OL,16,Fthe ballot, which closes on July 22 at
OL,17,F12pm.
