OL,3,CStrike ballot launched at university
OL,4,Cover proposed job cuts
OL,6,FIt comes in response to the UWS's
OL,7,FOrganisational Change Project, which
OL,8,Faims to cut around 75 full-time
OL,9,Fequivalent roles.
OL,11,FThe union says discussions with
OL,12,Funiversity bosses have been largely
OL,13,Funproductive, and that the employer
OL,14,Fhas shown a lack of transparency
OL,15,Fthroughout the process.
