OL,3,CStrike ballot launched at university
OL,4,Cover proposed job cuts
OL,6,FThe EIS said the university has
OL,7,Frefused to rule out compulsory
OL,8,Fredundancies, posing a threat to the
OL,9,Fjob security of its members and the
OL,10,Fquality of education, and added that
OL,11,Fit will have an overall detrimental
OL,12,Feffect on the UWS.
OL,14,FGarry Ross, EIS national officer for
OL,15,Fhigher education, condemned the
OL,16,Funiversity's approach.
