OL,3,CStrike ballot launched at university
OL,4,Cover proposed job cuts
OL,6,F"It is deeply regrettable that the
OL,7,FUniversity of the West of Scotland has
OL,8,Fchosen to make this large number of
OL,9,Fjob cuts and pushed staff to the point
OL,10,Fof balloting for strike action," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"The proposed redundancies are a short-
OL,14,Fsighted and a damaging strategy that
OL,15,Fwill have a devastating impact on the
OL,16,Flivelihoods of dedicated staff, many
OL,17,Fof whom have worked at UWS for years.
