OL,3,CStrike ballot launched at university
OL,4,Cover proposed job cuts
OL,6,F"Furthermore, it will inevitably lead
OL,7,Fto a decline in the academic
OL,8,Fprovision, research capacity, and
OL,9,Foverall student experience at the
OL,10,Funiversity.
OL,12,F"We urge UWS to step back from this
OL,13,Fpath and engage meaningfully with the
OL,14,FEIS ULA to secure a no compulsory
OL,15,Fredundancy guarantee."
OL,17,FA UWS spokesperson said: "We have
OL,18,Fsought to engage with our recognised
OL,19,Ftrade union representatives ahead of
OL,20,Fand throughout this process, including
OL,21,Fthe invitation to participate fully.
