OL,6,F"Having been disappointed previously
OL,7,Fwhen the recognised trade unions
OL,8,Fwithdrew their engagement, we provided
OL,9,Fan open invitation to return and
OL,10,Fcontribute to shaping the future of
OL,11,FUWS.
OL,13,F"We are pleased that this week they
OL,14,Freturned to the table to join the
OL,15,Funiversity in identifying approaches
OL,16,Fto avoiding compulsory redundancy,
OL,17,Fwith a number of proposals having
OL,18,Falready been tabled.
