OL,6,F"Our approach has been transparent
OL,7,Ffrom the outset and we have actively
OL,8,Fsought to co-create, with colleagues
OL,9,Fand trade union partners, a business
OL,10,Fcase to address ongoing student
OL,11,Fpopulation pressures, the challenging
OL,12,Fexternal funding environment and the
OL,13,Fresultant financial consequences being
OL,14,Ffelt across the entire sector."
